      "description": "This exceptional vehicle is the definition of turn-key perfection. Presenting in flawless mint condition, every inch of this car reflects meticulous care \u2014 from the spotless, blemish-free exterior finish to the pristine, like-new interior that still carries that fresh, factory feel. Mechanically sound and road-ready, it has been maintained to the highest standards with a clean history to match. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that truly stands apart from the crowd. Don't let it pass you by.",
